{"tid":1027713,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得足球同籃球呢兩種運動當中，身體質素定意識重要","createTime":"2019-02-19T03:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T06:37:00.000Z","uid":212151,"like":362,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"9d60e5321eca64a6fc38170308cd917626dc5f5a","tid":1027713,"uid":212151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"足球同籃球呢d團體性運動，有好多對抗，節奏又快，體能要求高，所以身體質素例如速度，彈跳力呢d會被視為重要條件。但係我睇左咁多NBA,西甲歐聯世界盃覺得一隊波唔需要全部都體能爆標，但係全隊嘅意識(走位，遮線，視野，理解球場嘅spacing，do the right thing at the right moment)必須要水準以上先可以有teamwork play. 見到香港d學界空有速度夠哂大隻但就睇唔到隊友喺邊就好笑，做佢地d隊友真係會走位走到頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身體質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4ad5ca39e30fff3d4a8c23e3108690050760aa","tid":1027713,"uid":98223,"like":65,"dislike":46,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"又公開處刑玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806ad930e1eeb471ba0ac99367f1684ca7297b92","tid":1027713,"uid":44954,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搏盡無悔</span></span>"},{"pid":"cac43eccf2bef6ff722d1acd8bf7c9d544e340da","tid":1027713,"uid":94828,"like":139,"dislike":85,"score":54,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"藍波呢啲猩猩運動唔使用腦<br />\n梗係身體質素重要<br />\n足球講球戰略冋團隊合作<br />\n用少啲腦都唔得咪意識囉"},{"pid":"00b64e7a294a8b9e4e51b41760180b5779399d07","tid":1027713,"uid":50658,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"ac4ad5ca39e30fff3d4a8c23e3108690050760aa","tid":1027713,"uid":98223,"like":65,"dislike":46,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"又公開處刑玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"文盲"},{"pid"